{"type": "article", "id": 24450, "title": "像桌布一样的家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-25T07:00:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606161159PWor7Re2x0X8h5Oy.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组桌子像是一张桌布，它是方形的，平整光滑，四个角都有小的折叠感。桌面下是纤细的金属结构，与桌面在材料和颜色上都产生对比，突出了桌面的轻盈，像是变魔术的道具。他们另有一款八边形的玻璃桌，支撑结构类似但更有棱角，玻璃桌面的边缘处有一些重叠的颜色，是想模拟钻石与光线之间的感觉。<a href=\"http://www.debrafolz.com/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061611565AMtazg4L1KSX28e.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061611570ku6t9hrGiEDaLs1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061611570UlKPHqkvrAFmBtz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061611583PF8QUhqiYX61Elu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060616115818mcvMPpQBSwx0lN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}